OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fsunny evening away from coasts.
OL,7,FLengthy clear spells overnight will
OL,8,Fallow areas of fog and low cloud to
OL,9,Fdevelop, with frost likely especially
OL,10,Fin prone rural spots. Cloud may linger
OL,11,Fnear coastal parts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA chilly start once again,
OL,14,Fwith early frost, fog and low cloud
OL,15,Fsoon clearing to leave another dry and
OL,16,Fsunny day. Remaining cooler near
OL,17,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
