OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FLargely
OL,6,Fdry during this period, with some
OL,7,Fsunny spells likely. Risk of overnight
OL,8,Ffog and frost. Often cool near coasts,
OL,9,Fbut warm inland.
